WEBVTT

00:05.280 --> 00:07.669
And now you're happy to
let me hang alongside you,

00:07.800 --> 00:10.314
when I bust my ass in here
to free you?

00:10.440 --> 00:13.273
Francis Thatcher is gone to exhume
the body of Robin Sumner.

00:14.440 --> 00:16.113
(GUNSHOT)

00:17.280 --> 00:20.113
LONG SUSAN:
All who kill must be punished.

00:20.240 --> 00:22.277
I wish to surrender myself
to the police.

00:22.400 --> 00:25.153
And I too wish to surrender myself
to the police.

00:25.280 --> 00:26.634
For what crime?

00:26.760 --> 00:28.592
Murder.

00:28.720 --> 00:30.199
I do not know you, sir.

00:32.560 --> 00:33.959
Who is this boy?

00:34.080 --> 00:35.275
- Gustus.
- (GUN COCKS)

00:35.400 --> 00:37.152
You know.

00:38.960 --> 00:41.952
Take control of your station house,
Inspector!

00:42.080 --> 00:44.515
Your voice makes me want to shit!

00:52.440 --> 00:53.999
(RAISED VOICES)

00:57.760 --> 00:59.558
ABBERLINE: That's right, Constable.

00:59.680 --> 01:02.638
All Whitechapel stands agog.

01:02.760 --> 01:06.116
Most like, Scotland Yard sends
a battalion to free their chief.

01:06.240 --> 01:09.119
Be calm, lad. You be calm.

01:09.240 --> 01:10.913
(RAISED VOICES OUTSIDE)

01:13.160 --> 01:14.434
But I seen it.

01:17.280 --> 01:19.476
I seen Gustus kill him.

01:19.600 --> 01:23.480
He witnessed Sergeant Thatcher shot,
Mr Drummond. I believe him.

01:24.880 --> 01:27.679
And who is he, that we should
give his word credence?

01:28.880 --> 01:30.553
Who are you, an' all, Miss Hart?

01:30.680 --> 01:32.114
(GATE CREAKS)

01:32.240 --> 01:33.992
In!

01:34.120 --> 01:35.918
(GUN COCKS)

01:36.040 --> 01:38.839
You're gonna leave her be, Drummond.

01:40.120 --> 01:41.793
Then you shoot me now, Captain,

01:41.920 --> 01:44.719
because this is either done
by the law or it is not.

01:45.960 --> 01:48.998
You let him do his job, Captain,
and he shall let you do yours.

01:49.120 --> 01:51.839
It is only you can make this case.

01:54.040 --> 01:55.075
(GUN CLICKS)

01:59.720 --> 02:01.358
(SNIFFS)

02:01.480 --> 02:03.790
(CROWD SHOUTS OUTSIDE)

02:08.639 --> 02:11.712
That was my Uncle Bennet's chair,

02:11.840 --> 02:14.832
and before it was his
it was my father's.

02:16.800 --> 02:19.235
(CHAINS CLINK)

02:23.000 --> 02:24.115
Inspector Drummond.

02:24.240 --> 02:26.550
Are you returned to your authority?

02:26.680 --> 02:28.273
Have you prevailed?

02:29.880 --> 02:31.279
(CROWD SHOUTS OUTSIDE)

02:31.400 --> 02:32.674
Leave us.

02:34.680 --> 02:37.832
Now, you wish to make your case.

02:37.960 --> 02:39.234
You go on, then, Tilda.

02:41.320 --> 02:43.709
The man in the cells beneath...

02:43.840 --> 02:47.117
he who says he is your brother,
I am going to interview him.

02:49.040 --> 02:50.155
Drummond?

02:50.280 --> 02:53.238
MATHILDA: I am going to
make written record of it.

02:54.360 --> 02:56.590
You will release me, Inspector.

02:59.880 --> 03:01.553
Now!

